### TapPass API Examples

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/health

### Register a Tag
POST http://localhost:3000/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tagHash": "0x1234567890abcdef1234567890abcdef1234567890abcdef1234567890abcdef",
  "wallet": "0x742d35Cc6634C0532925a3b844Bc9e7595f0bEb0"
}

### Get Tag Info
GET http://localhost:3000/tag/0x1234567890abcdef1234567890abcdef1234567890abcdef1234567890abcdef

### Mint Registration Pass
POST http://localhost:3000/mint/registration
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "wallet": "0x742d35Cc6634C0532925a3b844Bc9e7595f0bEb0"
}

### Mint Event Ticket
POST http://localhost:3000/mint/ticket
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "wallet": "0x742d35Cc6634C0532925a3b844Bc9e7595f0bEb0"
}

### Mint POAP
POST http://localhost:3000/mint/poap
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "wallet": "0x742d35Cc6634C0532925a3b844Bc9e7595f0bEb0"
}

### Get All Token Balances
GET http://localhost:3000/balance/0x742d35Cc6634C0532925a3b844Bc9e7595f0bEb0

### Get Specific Token Balance (1=REGISTRATION_PASS, 2=EVENT_TICKET, 3=EVENT_POAP)
GET http://localhost:3000/balance/0x742d35Cc6634C0532925a3b844Bc9e7595f0bEb0/1

